Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for TaiDoc FORA and Ultra Trak Active blood glucose monitoring systems using electrochemical method for quantitative measurement of glucose in whole blood
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from finger and alternative sites to aid diabetes management by healthcare professionals and patients at home; not for diagnosis or screening, nor for neonates
